OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPetrol: BP says UK fuel    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fshortages seem to be       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fstabilising                
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, BP has said that the fuel problems     
OL,6, caused by a shortage of HGV drivers is 
OL,7, starting to ease.                      
OL,9,FThe oil firm said long queues on its   
OL,10,Fforecourts "appear to be stabilising"  
OL,11,Fand that it is starting to see a small 
OL,12,Frise in stock across its network.      
OL,14,FBP was the first company to warn it had
OL,15,Fto close some petrol stations due to a 
OL,16,Fshortage of drivers, which has worsened
OL,17,Fdue to Covid and Brexit.               
OL,19,FThere are about 1,200 BP branded petrol
OL,20,Fstations around the UK.                
